{"tid":1109234,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃心穎的士攬啜許志安　黃爸爸咁樣講","createTime":"2019-04-16T08:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T08:43:24.000Z","uid":88491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e63b71c6863c12d3db00f17bf3e9f5d47602984b","tid":1109234,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ieyxyXX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FieyxyXX.png&h=a163087e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藝人黃心穎驚爆搭上歌手許志安，心穎任中醫師的父親今接受電話訪問，他指自己只看台灣新聞，對女兒攬啜許志安一事全不知情，他說：「我乜嘢都唔知道，亦唔想知，係咁。」然後便匆匆收線。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c178d2e659386e07125f53641f6ed3c9a61783f","tid":1109234,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:26:14.000Z","msg":"搞人屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffa72ac3ee9d2b8e82810e5d37217d6328f9d52","tid":1109234,"uid":245064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c178d2e659386e07125f53641f6ed3c9a61783f","tid":1109234,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:26:14.000Z","msg":"搞人屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:27:40.000Z","msg":"一人得道,全家升仙"},{"pid":"d54c832056612424d0e95a98694311a4cf4412ab","tid":1109234,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T08:43:24.000Z","msg":"搞台獨 等睇大陸網軍收你皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}